    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264640/extras/e5ff3ab413510442f204759ef6e1d0df.poster.avif?t=1759248291\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264640/extras/e5ff3ab413510442f204759ef6e1d0df.webm?t=1759248291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264640/extras/e5ff3ab413510442f204759ef6e1d0df.mp4?t=1759248291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backyard Digger is a relaxing physics-based game about digging in your backyard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover what lies beneath your lawn — there’s more than just dirt waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mine precious metals, uncover hidden treasures, and explore abandoned mines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell your finds to upgrade your tools so you can dig deeper, faster, and more efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for dangers like falling rocks, scorching heat, and the risk of crashing as you descend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How deep can you go? Uncover the secrets waiting at the bottom of Backyard Digger!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264640/extras/d529557529535c157fbd868283fb2962.poster.avif?t=1759248291\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264640/extras/d529557529535c157fbd868283fb2962.webm?t=1759248291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264640/extras/